    <div class="teaser__body">
      <header class="teaser__header">
                  <span class="meta teaser__taxonomy-label">  <span>Expert comment</span>
</span>
                <h3 class="h4 teaser__title"><span property="schema:name">US-China relations: Turning crisis into opportunity?</span>
</h3>
      </header>

              <div class="teaser__summary">
            <p>There is a window of opportunity for both countries to find common ground.</p>


        </div>
      
              <footer class="meta teaser__meta">
                      <span class="teaser__meta-date">  <time datetime="2021-03-26T12:00:00Z">26 March 2021</time>

 </span>
          
                              <span class="teaser__meta-read-time">3 minute READ</span>
                  
        </footer>
          </div>
  </a>
</article>


        </div>
              <div class="l-grid__item">
          

<article  about="/2021/03/battle-lines-being-drawn-over-online-freedoms-asia" typeof="schema:Article" class="teaser teaser--hide-summary">
  <a href="/2021/03/battle-lines-being-drawn-over-online-freedoms-asia" class="no-external-link-icon teaser__link">
    <div class="teaser__image-container">
        
  


  <div  class="media media-teaser_landscape media-image aspect-ratio-16:9">
                        <img class="lazyload" data-sizes="auto" data-srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/16_9_media_tiny/public/2021-03/GettyImages-936613164.jpg?h=c6980913&amp;itok=Pj_kJrrc 400w, /sites/default/files/styles/16_9_media_small/public/2021-03/GettyImages-936613164.jpg?h=c6980913&amp;itok=FgKieCU- 750w, /sites/default/files/styles/16_9_media_medium/public/2021-03/GettyImages-936613164.jpg?h=c6980913&amp;itok=pKP1PY_0 1000w, /sites/default/files/styles/16_9_media_large/public/2021-03/GettyImages-936613164.jpg?h=c6980913&amp;itok=rrw3yvBG 1300w" alt="Sharing an iPhone selfie from the campus of Wuhan University, Hubei Province, China. Photo by Wang HE/Getty Images." typeof="foaf:Image" />

      <noscript>
