    <div class="teaser__body">
      <header class="teaser__header">
                  <span class="meta teaser__taxonomy-label">  <span>Expert comment</span>
</span>
                <h3 class="h4 teaser__title"><span property="schema:name">Battle lines being drawn over online freedoms in Asia</span>
</h3>
      </header>

              <div class="teaser__summary">
            <p>Social media giants are increasingly clashing with Asian governments over free expression and censorship as the region lurches towards digital authoritarianism.</p>


        </div>
      
